<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>How it Works - BroqInsta Step-by-Step Production Guide</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <meta name="description" content="Step-by-step guide to downloading Instagram videos, reels, and photos with BroqInsta in 3 simple steps.">
    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= siteUrl %>/how-it-works">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:title" content="How it Works - BroqInsta Step-by-Step Production Guide">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Step-by-step guide to downloading Instagram videos, reels, and photos with BroqInsta in 3 simple steps.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="<%= siteUrl %>/images/preview.png">
    <meta property="og:url" content="<%= siteUrl %>/how-it-works">
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="BroqInsta">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="How it Works - BroqInsta Step-by-Step Production Guide">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Step-by-step guide to downloading Instagram videos, reels, and photos with BroqInsta in 3 simple steps.">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= siteUrl %>/images/preview.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        .step-number {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7C3AED, #EC4899);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .timeline-connector {
            position: absolute;
            top: 48px;
            left: 24px;
            bottom: -80px;
            width: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #7C3AED, #EC4899, transparent);
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .step-visual {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 3rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }

        .step-card:hover .step-visual {
            transform: scale(1.05) rotate(2deg);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-[#FAFBFC] min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <div class="hero-background">
        <div class="gradient-orb orb-1"></div>
        <div class="gradient-orb orb-2" style="right: auto; left: 60%; top: -10%;"></div>
        <div class="gradient-orb orb-3"></div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-5xl">
        <nav class="mb-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
            <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList">
                <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
                    <a href="/" itemprop="item" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors"><span itemprop="name">Home</span></a>
                    <meta itemprop="position" content="1">
                </li>
                <li><span class="mx-2">/</span></li>
                <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
                    <span itemprop="name" class="text-gray-600">How It Works</span>
                    <meta itemprop="position" content="2">
                </li>
            </ol>
        </nav>

        <div class="text-center mb-32 stagger-in">
            <h1 class="text-64px font-black text-gray-900 mb-6 italic">Simple as 1-2-3.</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed">
                We've spent thousands of hours perfecting the technology so you can save content in seconds.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-32">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center step-card">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 space-y-8 stagger-in">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="step-number">1</div>
                        <div class="timeline-connector"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900">Secure Link Acquisition</h2>
                        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                            Navigate to Instagram and find the content you wish to preserve. Use the platform's native
                            share feature to Copy the direct URL to your clipboard.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full animate-on-scroll">
                    <div class="step-visual text-8xl flex items-center justify-center">🔗</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-16 items-center step-card">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 space-y-8 stagger-in">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="step-number">2</div>
                        <div class="timeline-connector"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900">Advanced Edge Detection</h2>
                        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                            Paste the link into the BroqInsta dashboard. Our systems instantly perform a secure
                            handshake with the media servers to verify content availability.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full animate-on-scroll">
                    <div class="step-visual text-8xl flex items-center justify-center">⚡</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center step-card">
                <div class="md:w-1/2 space-y-8 stagger-in">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900">HD Bitrate Extraction</h2>
                        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                            Review your content and click Download. Our servers relay the highest available resolution
                            directly to your device with zero additional compression.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 w-full animate-on-scroll">
                    <div class="step-visual text-8xl flex items-center justify-center">🎥</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-48 text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="glass-card inline-block p-12 max-w-2xl bg-gray-900 text-white border-none">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Ready to Experience Elite Performance?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 text-lg">Join thousands of creators who use BroqInsta for professional
                    media management.</p>
                <a href="/" class="btn-primary px-12 py-6 text-xl shadow-glow">Start Your First Download</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>